{"tid":2440844,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"2男女分別藏士巴拿及索帶離開理大 今獲撤控簽保守行為2年","createTime":"2021-03-10T08:45:39.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-10T13:13:24.000Z","uid":240362,"like":10,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":23,"replies":[{"pid":"ef96de9bb24ee1952828a99b2287ba7df54218c2","tid":2440844,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-10T08:45:39.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://t.me/youarenotalonehk_live/14286\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fyouarenotalonehk_live%2F14286&d=QSug7dhZHD7voFbR5lwplR0Z1crOiE0eyIPSb4MeDzY%3D&h=c0f20f64\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/youarenotalonehk_live/14286</a><br />\n<br />\n#九龍城裁判法院第一庭<br />\n#鄭念慈裁判官<br />\n#1118尖沙咀 #提堂 <br />\n<br />\n祝 (16)<br />\n<br />\n控罪：管有適合作非法用途的工具並意圖作非法使用<br />\n<br />\n案情：<br />\n2019年11月19日在尖沙咀科學館及康達徑交界管有一個士巴拿。<br />\n<br />\n詳細案情（省略廢話）：<br />\n被告和其他人從理大方向接近註冊處，PW1為女性搜身，2030分搜查被告背包，搜到士巴拿。被告亦沒出示身份證明物件，以暴動,管有攻擊性武器,沒遵從指示出示身份證明文件拘捕。<br />\n<br />\n⭕️守行為24個月⭕️<br />\n自簽$2000<br />\n不得干犯同類案件<br />\n證物1-2充公"},{"pid":"0ae758c19a792386a9654acb5a4d5e0be72066b8","tid":2440844,"uid":240362,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-10T08:46:10.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://t.me/youarenotalonehk_live/14288\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fyouarenotalonehk_live%2F14288&d=QSug7dhZHD7voFbR5lwplR0Z1crOiE0eyIPSb4MeDzY%3D&h=f4278c92\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/youarenotalonehk_live/14288</a><br />\n<br />\n#九龍城裁判法院第一庭<br />\n#鄭念慈裁判官<br />\n#1117紅磡 #提堂 <br />\n<br />\n溫(25)<br />\n<br />\n控罪：管有適合作非法用途的工具並意圖作非法使用<br />\n<br />\n案情：<br />\n2019年11月17日，在加士居道近女童軍總會外管有2條膠索帶<br />\n<br />\n詳細案情（省略廢話）：<br />\n47名人士由理大步行向加士居道的防線，之後被截停，當中包括被告，被告被以暴動罪拘捕，警誡下保持緘默。<br />\n<br />\n⭕️守行為24個月⭕️<br />\n自簽$2000，訟費$500<br />\n充公2條膠條"},{"pid":"2ce3f5b3b9faebd0deb52a7f23251a898fc7778e","tid":2440844,"uid":230530,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2021-03-10T08:48:11.000Z","msg":"我有冇睇錯？？鄭生？"},{"pid":"b82f7de2c6105cce74f10fba2dc10730060f5fb4","tid":2440844,"uid":302471,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-10T08:48:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/notcry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/notcry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/notcry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"119fbbe070478ce1990ca0af88c59a8739a6d0a4","tid":2440844,"uid":238214,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-10T08:49:20.000Z","msg":"<strong><span class=\"red\">一定要保持緘默</span></strong>"},{"pid":"c8b7a8e693a05c2af659f2a5fad738f1ba3217e8","tid":2440844,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2ce3f5b3b9faebd0deb52a7f23251a898fc7778e","tid":2440844,"uid":230530,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2021-03-10T08:48:11.000Z","msg":"我有冇睇錯？？鄭生？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-10T08:49:27.000Z","msg":"律政司決定嘛"},{"pid":"40bdaedd48972d765341c5b87499ceabe32a014a","tid":2440844,"uid":78947,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-10T08:51:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ff0685bff7acbcd47567bbbfde40eeef1775aaf3","tid":2440844,"uid":281899,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2ce3f5b3b9faebd0deb52a7f23251a898fc7778e","tid":2440844,"uid":230530,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2021-03-10T08:48:11.000Z","msg":"我有冇睇錯？？鄭生？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-10T08:51:56.000Z","msg":"撤控就唔係佢決定"},{"pid":"c07af09ec8b53e9f9cce972eddc4a80db7c41b02","tid":2440844,"uid":21545,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2ce3f5b3b9faebd0deb52a7f23251a898fc7778e","tid":2440844,"uid":230530,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2021-03-10T08:48:11.000Z","msg":"我有冇睇錯？？鄭生？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-10T08:52:10.000Z","msg":"同佢無關<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.